/**
 * Grid config per card:
 * Mobile (2-col grid):  mobileCol × mobileRow
 * Desktop (3-col grid): desktopCol × desktopRow
 *
 * Mobile layout visual:
 * ┌──────────────┬──────────────┐  row 1-2
 * │   Card 1     │   Card 1     │  (2×2)
 * │              │              │
 * ├──────────────┼──────────────┤  row 3
 * │   Card 2     │   Card 3     │  (1×1 each)
 * ├──────────────┼──────────────┤  row 4-5
 * │   Card 4     │   Card 5     │  Card 4: 1×2, Card 5: 1×1
 * │   (tall)     ├──────────────┤
 * │              │   Card 6     │  row 5
 * ├──────────────┴──────────────┤  row 6
 * │         Card 7              │  (2×1)
 * └─────────────────────────────┘
 */